channel.title: How do I make .png files .jag for server?
channel.description: I accidently converted some .jag files from my server into .png, and I can't switch them back. They work when I click them, although they get messed up and some skill icons don't show. (The ones i accidently turned into .png) If anyone can help me with this, it would be greatly appreciated.
